title: MOJA - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents MOJA performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 8, 2023. 

Songs:
Geji Geji
NoThankYou
Hello

Haru- Bass, Vocals
Masumi - Drums

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
